metadata.name: I ATE IN MY DREAM
metadata.description:
I ate in my dream again!
Why?
Was it because I'm on diet?
Or was it because have been craving a particular food for a while?
Narrated my dream and someone said it's spiritually bad
Should I be scared? 
Are the demons after me?
Have you eaten in your dream too?
I have many questions but the meal was good.
